{"issuance_frequency":"","notes_translated":{"fr":"Les dispositifs mobiles se sont propagés rapidement dans les environnements ministériels du gouvernement du Canada (GC), et bien qu’ils permettent d’augmenter la productivité et l’efficacité, ils contribuent de façon notable à accroître le risque de compromission de l’information sensible. Pour atténuer cette nouvelle menace, le Centre de la sécurité des télécommunications Canada (CSTC) recommande aux ministères de déployer des solutions de gestion de dispositifs mobiles (MDM pour Mobile Device Management).\r\n","en":"Mobile devices have spread rapidly across the Government of Canada (GC) corporate enterprise and while they boost productivity and efficiency, they significantly increase the risk of a compromise to sensitive information. To help mitigate this threat, Communications Security Establishment Security Canada (CSEC) recommends departments utilize a Mobile Device Management (MDM) solution.\r\n"},"issn":"","imso_approval":"true","isbn":"","creator":"","org_section":{"fr":"Centre canadien pour la cybersécurité (CCC)","en":"Canadian Centre for Cyber Security (CCCS)"},"jurisdiction":"federal","private":false,"maintainer_email":"open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca","num_tags":0,"edition":"","frequency":"not_planned","data_series_issue_identification":{"fr":"","en":""},"contributor":{"fr":"","en":""},"maintainer":null,"ready_to_publish":"true","id":"40fe3c70-7de8-4db8-b276-35921df72a24","metadata_created":"2019-12-12T21:43:56.172723","subject":["information_and_communications","science_and_technology"],"pspc_identification_number":"","metadata_modified":"2019-12-12T21:43:56.172731","author":null,"author_email":null,"geographic_region":[],"portal_release_date":"2019-12-12","digital_object_identifier":"","state":"active","version":null,"keywords":{"fr":["Mobilité"],"en":["Mobility"]},"relationships_as_object":[],"creator_user_id":"4cfa9a9c-1d95-40eb-86f9-bc0c8ec45d1f","title_translated":{"fr":"Solutions de gestion de disposit